{"tid":1025274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為高層放話不稀罕澳紐巿場 稱澳洲還不及廣州","createTime":"2019-02-17T08:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T02:42:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":265,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"399a4a0736b9a75a4527d638e60e370ff80ab061","tid":1025274,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T08:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2270000/2272918/1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2270000%2F2272918%2F1_1024.jpg&h=792f0658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前多個國家都表明抵制華為，指不會使用華為的 5G 設備和技術。未知華為是否心有不甘，還是要還擊，早前高層便指美國呼籲盟友的抵制行動，對其全球業務的影響微乎其微，又指澳洲和紐西蘭的巿場很小，還不及廣州。<br />\n<br />\n德國 5G 拒完封華為<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧出訪中歐，向匈牙利、斯洛伐克和波蘭等多國施壓，呼籲不要使用華為等中國電訊設備。日前，華為副董事長徐直軍發言，指責美國在組織一場有預謀的打壓，認為美方不是出於安全考慮，而是另有動機，例如擔心某些國家選擇採用華為設備，變相令美國難以取得這些國家的數據。<br />\n<br />\n同時，徐直軍回應在澳紐發展遇上的問題時，直指：「澳大利亞市場還不如廣州的市場大，新西蘭市場也不如我的老家大。所以，我認為就算我們不出現在某些國家也無所謂。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2272918\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2272918&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxmipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=dab0bdef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2272918</a>"},{"pid":"a47fcf64ab5ab6f8812398fd8af34cecc6468fc7","tid":1025274,"uid":74778,"like":141,"dislike":2,"score":139,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T08:35:30.000Z","msg":"向世界開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後鎖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65e2ee9ce3878e042f6cb581a935f6a9ad62242","tid":1025274,"uid":188421,"like":124,"dislike":3,"score":121,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T08:37:09.000Z","msg":"德國到底係到諗咩"},{"pid":"c9050d32fffbec1f449b34d1fc879c297a8e852b","tid":1025274,"uid":152476,"like":87,"dislike":3,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T08:43